  <brief_title>A Post Market Study Evaluating the Safety, Device Perfomance and Possible Emergent Risks of Celotres in Preventing Recurrence in Keloid Lesions Treated Adjunctive to Surgical Excision</brief_title>
  <acronym>EURO KLEAR</acronym>
  <official_title>A Post Market Study Evaluating the Safety, Device Perfomance and Possible Emergent Risks of Celotres in Preventing Recurrence in Keloid LEsions Treated Adjunctive to suRgical Excision. PMCS: EURO-KLEAR</official_title>
